import React from 'react';
import { Container, Row, Col, Card } from 'react-bootstrap';

const Home = () => {
  return (
    <Container fluid>
      <Row>
        <Col md={3}>
          <Card className="text-center mb-4">
            <Card.Body>
              <Card.Title>Total Income</Card.Title>
              <Card.Text>$14,025</Card.Text>
            </Card.Body>
          </Card>
        </Col>
        <Col md={3}>
          <Card className="text-center mb-4">
            <Card.Body>
              <Card.Title>Sessions</Card.Title>
              <Card.Text>2025</Card.Text>
            </Card.Body>
          </Card>
        </Col>
        <Col md={3}>
          <Card className="text-center mb-4">
            <Card.Body>
              <Card.Title>Ethereum Wallet</Card.Title>
              <Card.Text>8025</Card.Text>
            </Card.Body>
          </Card>
        </Col>
        <Col md={3}>
          <Card className="text-center mb-4">
            <Card.Body>
              <Card.Title>Number of Clients</Card.Title>
              <Card.Text>5645</Card.Text>
            </Card.Body>
          </Card>
        </Col>
      </Row>
      <Row>
        <Col md={8}>
          <Card className="mb-4">
            <Card.Body>
              <Card.Title>Sales Overview</Card.Title>
              <Card.Text>Chart goes here...</Card.Text>
            </Card.Body>
          </Card>
        </Col>
        <Col md={4}>
          <Card className="mb-4">
            <Card.Body>
              <Card.Title>Your Portfolio</Card.Title>
              <Card.Text>Portfolio details go here...</Card.Text>
            </Card.Body>
          </Card>
        </Col>
      </Row>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default Home;
